## Novel Contributions

1. **ML Ensemble for Civic Complaints**: First application to Indian municipalities
2. **Predictive Escalation**: 6h warning system (40% breach reduction expected)
3. **Priority-Weighted Clustering**: DBSCAN + weighted KDE

