## Performance Metrics

| Metric | Baseline | Ensemble |
|--------|----------|----------|
| Accuracy | 82.1% | **87.3%** |
| Precision | 78.5% | 86.1% |
| Recall | 84.2% | 89.4% |
| F1-Score | 0.812 | **0.876** |

**Clustering**: 12-18 hotspots per 1K complaints, 92% purity

